        "name": "Elemental Explosion",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You unleash the energy roiling within you, exploding elemental matter in a 15-foot emanation. Each creature in the area takes 1d8 damage per level you possess, with the same type you chose for elemental rage. Each creature in the area must attempt a basic Reflex save against your class DC. Elemental Explosion gains the trait of your element.",
